{"tid":1692563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"距離天琦書面裁決仲有六日","createTime":"2019-11-04T06:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:50:31.000Z","uid":27670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8f478ef48b62f6ea6036edee96ca0511c7cf93","tid":1692563,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"10月9號 法官話一個月內會出書面裁決<br />\n即係話呢幾日內就會有<br />\n唔係話放負 但係我覺得政府冇可能俾佢而家出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我甚至有d陰謀論覺得係因為預左判完之後大家會好嬲<br />\n所以趁呢幾日再癲d 打到起碼有一部份人唔夠膽出黎<br />\n<br />\n就算得0.000000001% 我都希望佢可以出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9a253f26a4fc434b32968231488dde911ed55a","tid":1692563,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"我有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}